<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />One thing have I asked of Yahweh, and I will seek that:</para>

<para style="q1">that I may live in the house of Yahweh all the days of my life,</para>

<para style="q1">to see the beauty of Yahweh</para>

<para style="q1">and to meditate in his temple.</para>
